comment: /** * Returns whether the checkpoint is in progress. * * @return true if checkpoint is in progress, false otherwise. */
code: /** * Returns whether the checkpoint is in progress. * * @return true if checkpoint is in progress, false otherwise. */ public boolean isInProgress() { return this == IN_PROGRESS. }

comment: /** * Returns whether the checkpoint has completed successfully. * * @return true if checkpoint has completed, false otherwise. */
code: /** * Returns whether the checkpoint has completed successfully. * * @return true if checkpoint has completed, false otherwise. */ public boolean isCompleted() { return this == COMPLETED. }

comment: /** * Returns whether the checkpoint has failed. * * @return true if checkpoint has failed, false otherwise. */
code: /** * Returns whether the checkpoint has failed. * * @return true if checkpoint has failed, false otherwise. */ public boolean isFailed() { return this == FAILED. }
